          "goals": [],
          "code": "<!--\n  title: 响应式设计\n  description: 媒体查询、视口单位、移动优先\n  goals: @media媒体查询; viewport单位vw/vh; 移动优先设计\n  tags: responsive, media-query\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>响应式设计</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: sans-serif; margin: 1rem; }\n    .container { padding: 1rem; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 8px; }\n    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }\n    .card { background: white; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; }\n    /* 平板 */\n    @media (min-width: 600px) {\n      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    }\n    /* 桌面 */\n    @media (min-width: 900px) {\n      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>响应式设计</h1>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <p>调整浏览器窗口大小查看变化：</p>\n    <div class=\"grid\">\n      <div class=\"card\"><h3>卡片1</h3><p>窄屏：单列</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card\"><h3>卡片2</h3><p>中屏：两列</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card\"><h3>卡片3</h3><p>宽屏：三列</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p>移动优先：先写小屏样式，再用 <code>@media</code> 扩展到大屏。</p>\n</body>\n</html>",
