          "description": "",
          "goals": [],
          "code": "<!--\n  title: CSS 过渡与动画\n  description: transition过渡、@keyframes关键帧动画、transform变换\n  goals: transition属性; @keyframes动画; transform变换\n  tags: animation, transition\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>CSS 过渡与动画</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 1rem; }\n    .hover-box { background: #059669; color: white; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 6px;\n                transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: pointer; }\n    .hover-box:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: #047857; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(5,150,105,0.3); }\n    @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.1); } }\n    .animated { animation: pulse 2s infinite; background: #d1fae5; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>CSS 过渡与动画</h1>\n  <h2>过渡 (transition)</h2>\n  <div class=\"hover-box\">鼠标悬停试试 → 缓慢放大变色</div>\n  <p><code>transition: all 0.3s ease</code> — 属性变化平滑过渡</p>\n  <h2>关键帧动画 (@keyframes)</h2>\n  <div class=\"animated\">持续脉动效果</div>\n  <p><code>@keyframes pulse</code> + <code>animation: pulse 2s infinite</code></p>\n</body>\n</html>",
